definition: from/through/via/to follow/to obey/to engage in (an activity)/never (in negative sentence)/(Taiwan pr. [zong4]) retainer/assistant/auxiliary/subordinate/related by common paternal grandfather or earlier ancestor
to hit (the mark)/to be hit by/to suffer/to win (a prize, a lottery)

sentences.english: But learn from them. They scale and serve millions of users.
sentences.chinese: 而是从中学习，他们服务于数以百万的用户。

sentences.english: Just keep looking at this progress of losing and regaining awareness and learn from it.
sentences.chinese: 只要保持观照这个觉知失而复得的过程，并从中学习。

sentences.english: This is a great good deed. The people involved can all benefit from it.
sentences.chinese: 这是件大好事，只要是参与的人都可以从中获益。

sentences.english: But we have learned from these efforts.
sentences.chinese: 但是，我们从中吸取了教训。

sentences.english: I know that I get around 90g of protein from that.
sentences.chinese: 我知道我会从中得到90克左右的蛋白质。

sentences.english: That was transported by and dropped from an iceberg.
sentences.chinese: 系由冰山搬运而来并从中坠下的。

sentences.english: From them we can see obviously what the compiler is emphasizing.
sentences.chinese: 从中明显可以看出诉述主体的失重态势。

sentences.english: Work with the best of intentions and gain your self respect from that.
sentences.chinese: 带着最好的意图工作并从中获得你的自我尊重吧。

sentences.english: Our galaxy's core is a frenzied place, and identifying baby stars there has been difficult.

sentences.english: They feel more comfortable and safe,” says Çiftçi. “It is also good for their families.
sentences.chinese: 老人们感到更舒适和更安全，其家人也可从中受益。

sentences.english: Consumers can then pick and choose how they want to interact with your brand.
sentences.chinese: 消费者可以从中筛选并选择如何与你的品牌进行互动。

sentences.english: It also points to the importance of internal incentives in a qualified official.
sentences.chinese: 从中也可看出一个合格的官员自我内在激励的重要性。

sentences.english: And what would i profit by that?
sentences.chinese: 那我又能从中得到什么好处？

sentences.english: All those objects are linked by opal glass, which allows light to penetrate all areas.
sentences.chinese: 它们都是通过乳色玻璃进行连接的，阳光可从中透过。

sentences.english: Although the training was really hard, it strengthened my will and Ive benefited a lot from it.
sentences.chinese: 尽管训练的确艰苦，但磨练了意志，我从中得益良多。

sentences.english: No, she would have taken it calmly, and found pleasures therein.
sentences.chinese: 不会，她只会泰然处之，而且还要从中找到乐趣。
